data.description: Beautiful recently remodeled Home along with 3.73 acres of land! Escape from all the busy City life commotion! Enjoy the serene and peaceful country living. 3 Bedrooms with Big Bonus room upstairs 2 full bath. Granite counter tops, Beautiful Ceramic floors on wet areas and laminate wood floors all throughout. Step outside onto the extended deck surrounded by Natures Beauty, great for Entertainment and relaxation. This one is a must see!
